whats the purpose for : org.apache.ignite.internal.client.GridClientCacheMode#LOCAL ?

@zstan @anton-vinogradov @isapego @ptupitsyn @NSAmelchev 

Folks, I've fixed all your comments. Please, take a final look.
Also added guarantee that both pools are blocked in backup node before killing the primary one.

The changes are similar to those of IGNITE-17274.  A new map is added to track the registered service-names mapped to the service-info structure.  The lookup is changed from a linear lookup of the `deployedService.values()` structure to a `get` on the new map.
The purpose (WHY) of this change is to improve service shutdown performance (in local testing 60,000 services, shutdown time dropped from around 60 seconds to around 1 second).
